{"tid":2056402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"慈雲山37m小巴站癲佬","createTime":"2020-06-08T15:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T16:02:50.000Z","uid":69372,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44e9d1e1a8ee7d5e472ddeca0c1de77a86c83f76","tid":2056402,"uid":69372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無遇過<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山37m小巴站，朝早成日有個男人好似趕羊咁喝啲乘客上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢應該係幫手喺站點人數上車嗰啲，但條友好似有燥狂症咁，有時又大大聲播歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有呢個時勢，都仲可以唔帶口罩真係好自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（但有時係個嬸嬸幫手，正常好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"c0b97d9ec79c873070f82b3ae9be7c7b50d35fa9","tid":2056402,"uid":69372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"係咪香港人壓力太大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3583e4824294706634338d23068dd97eb146a936","tid":2056402,"uid":140246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:22:59.000Z","msg":"站長呀。 白卡黎。"},{"pid":"edd3a60f9ade0a2531395d9999d8ee29b14ae3b5","tid":2056402,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:23:51.000Z","msg":"我見到個啲到正正常常"},{"pid":"dbeb9d9863068f6d858fdfd7670535a40a2c189d","tid":2056402,"uid":69372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd3a60f9ade0a2531395d9999d8ee29b14ae3b5","tid":2056402,"uid":27397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:23:51.000Z","msg":"我見到個啲到正正常常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:35:29.000Z","msg":"黃大仙上慈雲山嗰啲多數正常，最多係數錯人數搞到人再排過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但慈雲山朝早嗰條友真係唔多正常"},{"pid":"e632199d908094abdae7a48b51a4077abd84d682","tid":2056402,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"條友好似唔係真站長黎"},{"pid":"9b1c94719e3fad983ff9607578640da99bfed0a3","tid":2056402,"uid":69372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e632199d908094abdae7a48b51a4077abd84d682","tid":2056402,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"條友好似唔係真站長黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"即係自己行埋去扮站長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adb090b7ebbf8861355686104c7df1f9077f5b5","tid":2056402,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b1c94719e3fad983ff9607578640da99bfed0a3","tid":2056402,"uid":69372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e632199d908094abdae7a48b51a4077abd84d682","tid":2056402,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"條友好似唔係真站長黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:41:39.000Z","msg":"即係自己行埋去扮站長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"你拎白咭你都可以扮架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab3a8671386fe50942d7a279972c0abc9f63c7","tid":2056402,"uid":318051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b1c94719e3fad983ff9607578640da99bfed0a3","tid":2056402,"uid":69372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e632199d908094abdae7a48b51a4077abd84d682","tid":2056402,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,